### Create User (POST)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/account/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "testpass123"
}

###

### List Users - Unauthenticated (GET) - Should return 401
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/account/

###

### List Users - Authenticated (GET)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/account/
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get User Detail - Authenticated (GET)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/account/1/
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Update User - Owner (PUT)
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/account/1/
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updateduser",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

###

### Delete User - Owner (DELETE)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/account/1/
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

